## How we work

Explore in `exploratory/`, then package code into `src/` at the exploration boundary. Pipelines are code (re-runnable), not cleaned snapshots. Pin environments so others — and other agents — can reproduce results. <!-- IF:COLLAB -->Follow `CONTRIBUTING.md` for the branch/PR/review workflow and `CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md` for community norms.<!-- /IF -->
